yr</TD> <TD>structured</TD> <TD>Bear Stearns</TD> <TD>507bp</TD> </TR><P>
<TR><TD>Argentina</TD> <TD>Dm500m</TD> <TD>30 yr</TD> <TD>Eurobond</TD>
<TD>DMG</TD> <TD>497bp</TD> </TR><P> <TR><TD>Brazil</TD> <TD>$750 m</TD> <TD>5
yr</TD> <TD>global</TD> <TD>JP Morgan/SBCWarburg</TD> <TD>265bp</TD> </TR><P>
<TR><TD COLSPAN=6>Source: UBS, date order</TD> </TR><P> </TABLE> 

<p>
</td>
</tr>
