<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="images/logo2.gif" ALIGN=middle>
</center>
<BR>
<blockquote>

Welcome to the Bank of America pages on EMWL. 
<P> 

Bank of America is graded 'AA' by major credit agencies, and has total assets of $230
billion and total equity of more than $20 billion. 

<P> 

The bank has relationships with more than 90% of the Fortune 500 corporations and over 85% of the Fortune1,000.

<P>

Bank of America provides global commercial and investment banking services to
multinational companies, major indigeneous companies, financial institutions,
governments and government agencies worldwide. 

<P>

On the wholesale and international markets, Bank of America provides services in
credit and lending, capital raising, capital markets and cash management.


<P>

Outside the US, Bank of America delivers services through three international
divisions: Asia, Latin America & Canada, and Europe, Middle East & Africa. <P>


Bank of America on EMWL provides a detailed account of key services, offices and
contacts within these regions and provides a comprehensive news and analysis
profile through Hot News and Markets pages. <P> Please use the icons on
all of the Bank of America sections to navigate round the pages. They are
designed to help you find information that you are looking for quickly. The
icons
on the regional pages will lead you to region-specific information, but if you
nagivate from the Home Page, the links will lead you to the beginning of each
section. 
</blockquote>
<BR>
<P>
