<center> <font size=3>

<table border=0> <tr> <td align=right> <nobr> <a href="../../../index.html"
name="top"><img border=0 hspace=0 src="../images/spon1.gif"></a> </nobr> </td>
</tr>

<tr> <td align=middle> <img src="images/spon96001.gif"> <H1>Pakistan</H1>
<H4><i>Poised for Progress</i></H4> <H3 ALIGN="CENTER"> <B>General Rules Governing </B> </H3>
<H3 ALIGN="CENTER"> <B>Foreign Investment</B> </H3>
</td> </tr>

<tr> <td align=left> <blockquote>

<P> The laws of Pakistan are very liberal towards foreign direct or portfolio investment. A
foreign national can now own up to 100% equity in a company and is free to repatriate
his capital, capital gains as well as dividends, whenever he feels like.
Government permission is not required for investment in manufacturing concerns. 
Similarly, there is complete freedom of investment in stock markets.

<P> Foreign direct investment is also guaranteed protection against
nationalization and acquisition by the Government under the terms of Foreign
Private Investment (Protection &amp; Promotion) Act, 1977.

<P> The BOI has designed special packages of fiscal and monetary incentives for
the following industries:

<P> - Housing Sector

<P> - Petro-Chemical Industry 

<P> - Electronic Industry 

<P> - Manufacture of Fertilizers

<P> - Basic Manufacture of Pharmaceutical

<P> - Hotel &amp; Tourism Industry

<P> - Agro-Food Industry

<P> - Private Power Generation

<P> - Petroleum Exploration &amp; Production

<P> For more details on any of these packages, please contact the Board of Investment.


<P ALIGN="CENTER"> <B>BOARD OF INVESTMENT</B><BR>

<ALIGN="CENTER"> <B>GOVERNMENT OF PAKISTAN</B><BR>

<ALIGN="CENTER"> <B>12-13th Floor, Saudi Pak Tower, Jinnah Avenue</B><BR>

<ALIGN="CENTER"> <B>Islamabad, Pakistan</B><BR>

<ALIGN="CENTER"> <B>TEL: (92-51) 817165, 9218266, 9218267, 99202845, 9217507</B><BR>

<ALIGN="CENTER"> <B>FAX: (92-51) 9215554, 9217665, 9203281</B><BR>

<center>
<br>For more information, click on the colored text:<br><br>

<font size=3>
<nobr>
<b>
<a href="spon96001.html"> [ BOI Home ] </a><br>
