<HTML>
<!--created Oyster Systems-->
<!--May 1996-->
<HEAD>
<TITLE>
EMWL: IBC Introduction
</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<body background="images/backgd.gif" bgcolor="ff6600" vlink="CCCCCC" alink="ff6600" text="000000" link="FFFFFF">

<table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 border=0 width=100%>
<tr><td valign=top align=left>

<img border=0 width=72 height=247 src="images/sidetop.gif" alt="Graphic"><br><a href="intro.html"><img border=0 width=72 height=19 src="images/side1.gif" alt="Introduction"></a><br><a href="attend.html"><img border=0 width=72 height=20 src="images/side2.gif" alt="Attending"></a><br><a href="spon.html"><img border=0 width=72 height=20 src="images/side3.gif" alt="Sponsors"></a><br><a href="agend.html"><img border=0 width=72 height=20 src="images/side4.gif" alt="Agenda"></a><br><a href="exhibit.html"><img border=0 width=72 height=20 src="images/side5.gif" alt="Exhibiting"></a><br><a href="history.html"><img border=0 width=72 height=20 src="images/side6.gif" alt="History"></a><br><a href="more.html"><img border=0 width=72 height=21 src="images/side7.gif" alt="More Info"></a><br><a href="more.html"><img border=0 width=72 height=21 src="images/side9.gif" alt="Register"></a><br><a href="index.html"><img border=0 width=72 height=21 src="images/side8.gif" alt="Home"></a><br><br>

</td> 

<td>

<center>
<img  width=363 height=38 border=0 hspace=0 src="images/title1.gif" alt="Introduction">
</center>
<br><br>
<blockquote>
<font size=4><b>Introduction</b></font>
<ul>
The Third Euromoney International Bond Congress (IBC) will be held on the 25th & 26th February 1997 at the Queen Elizabeth II Conference Centre, London.
<br><br>
The IBC has become the premier event for the world's Bond Market Professionals. 
The Congress consists of a Forum and an Expo.
At the Forum all major aspects of the markets are discussed and debated 
by professionals.
<br><br>
The Expo consists of a mixture of hospitality suites and expo stands and is the market place where market participants meet face to face to initiate business, consolidate relationships and encourage investment.
<br><br>
With the experience and expertise developed from the previous two events, the 1997 IBC will be the largest and most effective to date.
<br><br>
</ul>
<font size=4><b>Features</b></font>
<ul>
<li> The Congress will last two days. A cocktail reception will be held at the end of the first day.
<li> There will be a wide range of hospitality suites, and expo stands for lead sponsors, co-sponsors and exhibitors.
<li> The Forum agenda will be researched and compiled with many of the markets' leading professionals. New subjects and concepts will be introduced to ensure the relevance and interest for those attending.
<li> High profile keynote speakers will begin each day.
<li> Leading economists, traders and investors will take part in interactive panel discussions.
<li> Access to the Expo is complimentary.
<li> Lunch and coffee will be served within the Expo area 
to allow delegates added opportunity to visit sponsors 
and exhibitors.
</ul><br><br>

</blockquote>
</blockquote>

</td></tr></table>

<center>
