<center>
<h2>
INTRODUCTION
</h2>
</center>

<BR>

<blockquote>

<ul>
<li> Created in 1822, Generale Bank is Belgium's leading bank in <b>commercial banking and investment banking</b>.<BR>
 Generale Bank is the cornerstone of a group comprising some <b>150 banks and companies</b> worldwide, employing 27,700 people 
<center>(see <a href="generale.5.html">X  NETWORK)</a></center>
<BR>
<li> Generale Bank was ranked 26th in Europe and 46th in the world in terms of total assets by the magazine "The Banker" in July 1996.
</ul>

</blockquote>

<BR>
