A video showing highlights from the World Economic Forum's 1996 Annual Meeting
in Davos is available at a cost of $49.95 ($5 p&amp;p). If you are interested
please contact Kate Charters, Location Specials Sales, Reuters Television
Ltd, 85 Fleet Street, London EC4P 4AJ. <BR>
